    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Trimming made by twisting silk, worsted, or cotton thread around a core thread or wire, resulting in a flat openwork braid.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
